branchCategory.name: C(D)BA2, Air Cylinder, Double Acting, Single Rod, End Lock
branchCategory.description: <p>Series CBA2 End Lock version of the light weight tie rod air cylinder. End of stroke locking mechanism locks the cylinder in place in case of a loss of air. Locks can be ordered for the extend stroke, retract stroke or both. The CA2 is available in a large variety of options that will make them suitable for many different applications. A variety of auto switches are available for mounting, including compact switches and magnetic field resistant switches. The CA2 is available in 40, 50, 63, 80 and 100 bores sizes, and is RoHS compliant</p>
